PULIS ON THE UP 

Tony Pulis has his strikers firing but, most importantly for West Brom, he has stopped them leaking goals. 

He builds teams from the back and it shows in the stats. 

At Palace last season they conceded far fewer goals after his arrival and it’s the same now at the Hawthorns. 

He’s such a specialist in the relegation scrap.

